nodes.agent_prompt:
Fetch details on the features of the Mahindra XUV 3XO vehicle. Refine your search query iteratively to gather comprehensive information about all features. Set call_self=true. Use the following JSON format:

```json
{
  "features": [
    {
      "feature_name": "Feature 1",
      "description": "Description of feature 1"
    },
    {
      "feature_name": "Feature 2",
      "description": "Description of feature 2"
    }
  ]
}
```
